response.overview: The Sixth installment of the popular Truck Tunes series delivers 10 more trucks and machines with 10 great new songs! These new music videos, featuring actual live footage of the machines at work are certain to have you laughing, dancing and singing along. Songs include, "Pumper", "Recreational Vehicle", "Mail Truck", "Road Zipper", "Grapple Truck" and more.  Kids of all ages will love these videos!
response.title: Truck Tunes 6
